489
00:39:09,930 --> 00:39:14,370
♫ Hug me sweetly ya, ya, ya ♫

490
00:39:14,370 --> 00:39:19,110
♫ everything will change ♫

491
00:39:19,110 --> 00:39:21,210
Yes?

492
00:39:21,210 --> 00:39:23,680
I'm sorry, but I don't think I'll be able to see you today.

493
00:39:23,680 --> 00:39:27,560
Are you going to keep doing this to me? You canceled on me last time, too!

494
00:39:27,560 --> 00:39:29,920
That's why we took a walk.

495
00:39:29,920 --> 00:39:32,810
I'm busy too, you know! I have to prepare for my demo classes

496
00:39:32,810 --> 00:39:35,140
and my girls are competing in a dance competition next month.

497
00:39:35,140 --> 00:39:38,450
So are you saying that that's more important than me?

498
00:39:38,450 --> 00:39:39,760
Of course.

499
00:39:39,760 --> 00:39:42,210
Let's forget about today and meet up on the weekend instead.

500
00:39:42,210 --> 00:39:45,870
This isn't a favor I'm asking of you. This is a request.

501
00:39:45,870 --> 00:39:49,440
♫ Nothing is easy ♫

502
00:39:54,980 --> 00:40:00,640
♫ Even though love is a common word  ♫

503
00:40:02,150 --> 00:40:07,480
♫ The one word I practice everyday ♫

504
00:40:07,480 --> 00:40:09,260
Are you sure our CEO is dating?

505
00:40:09,260 --> 00:40:11,610
According to the rumors, he is.

506
00:40:11,610 --> 00:40:13,600
When I asked to start over, I was serious.

507
00:40:13,600 --> 00:40:16,940
It's because Seon Wu said something weird. He said that the person you are seeing is rich.

508
00:40:16,940 --> 00:40:17,920
Can't you trust me?

509
00:40:17,920 --> 00:40:19,290
You little brat, stop it!

510
00:40:19,290 --> 00:40:20,990
Why did she freak out when she heard I was rich?

511
00:40:20,990 --> 00:40:23,320
I thought over it again and realized that there's no other man like you.

512
00:40:23,320 --> 00:40:24,840
I told you it's strictly business!

513
00:40:24,840 --> 00:40:25,700
Business?

514
00:40:25,700 --> 00:40:27,980
I made it clear to Mom that we're not getting married.

515
00:40:27,980 --> 00:40:29,990
I think we'll have to take some countermeasures.

516
